bles)\n    write_code \u0022DemoVisualization.fs\u0022 refactoredCode\n\n// Generate tests for the showSemanticMessage function\nlet generateTestsForShowSemanticMessage() =\n    generate_test { function = \u0022showSemanticMessage\u0022; module = \u0022DemoVisualizationTests\u0022; file = \u0022DemoVisualizationTests.fs\u0022 }\n\n// Run the test suite\nlet runTestSuite() =\n    run_tests { project = \u0022path/to/test.fsproj\u0022; filter = None }\n\u0060\u0060\u0060\n\n### Conclusion:\nBy following these steps, the F# codebase will be refactored to improve readability and maintainability while ensuring all original functionality is preserved. The use of provided tools ensures that each step is executed systematically and efficiently.\u0022\n     Timestamp = 2025-12-28 8:13:32 AM\n     Metadata = map [] }]",
